title: Henriques (Manuel António de Azevedo)
body: We have knowledge of this Madeiran from the little that the author of the Diccionario Bibliographico Portuguez tells us about him. He published in Lisbon, in 1778, a pamphlet of 47 pages, entitled Reino de Deus ou Reino de Portugal, Panegyrico Funchalense, offered... to D. Maria I and D. Pedro III.
